Bl41A">Tiền xuất tái kỳ 8 - 前出塞其八</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/T%C3%B2ng-qu%C3%A2n-h%C3%A0nh/poem-Bv3fj5d7fpE70_uRe8vB7g">Tòng quân hành - 從軍行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%BF-Trinh/author-K5yGjv4-gkyzXKfuttJFiQ">Vương Thế Trinh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-S%C3%B9ng/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-Sxhd0GyVC7qZhAkCaf0d6g">Vương Chiêu Quân từ - 王昭君辭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A1ch-S%C3%B9ng/author-Vp0DUW6qXKB_-T0oNli1fg">Thạch Sùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%B9-H%E1%BB%AFu/Xa-dao-dao/poem-9R2ta7R1tQXyQKJn-evZwg">Xa dao dao - 車遙遙</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%C3%B9-H%E1%BB%AFu/author-ZjSu27nDCKsyKWbOwBvzWw">Cù Hữu</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
